		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=140616"><span id=Sage>Victorex</span></a><b><span id=Sage><br>Sage</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>58 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.80]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Victorex&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>An excellent low cost alternative to the Crystal Covered Shroud is the Spore Covered Tunic. AC is identical, 1 less str, no wis or int, no saves, weighs 0.4 and you can find it for less than 50pp in EC. In fact I have seen it auctioned for as little as 15pp. If you don't want to go with the robe look and aren't concerned by the lack of int or wis, or you just don't have the 250pp to drop for the CCS, you can't go wrong with this tunic. It has a dark green look to it, and if you get smacked hard enough by a mob there is always the chance of it sneezing because of the spores flying off your body. :-)<br><br>Just thought of one other low cost alternative to Master Niteklaw's list, face item - Silvery mask. 1 less ac than the sarnak mask, but +25hps and you can find them for less than 100pp. Also has an effect - unlimited charges of identify. Might be useful in some situations where a guildmate or a friend has a quest item that needs to be identified (ivy etched and bard coin quests come to mind) to keep from turning in the wrong item and losing it (GM's will NOT be sympathetic and return the item to you, you will have to start all over on the quest). All in all, a very nice item for the price and might allow you to get one of the other nice pieces on Master Niteklaw's list without breaking the bank.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Apr&nbsp;&nbsp;9 14:47:10 2002</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Jheran 54 Human Monk<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=310212" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=310212<